# overview.md
msgid "Unio Documentation"
msgstr "Unio 文档"

msgid ""
"These documents describe the Unio system after the from-zero refactor."
msgstr "本文档描述从零重构后的 Unio 系统。"

msgid "Recommended reading order:"
msgstr "推荐阅读顺序："

msgid ""
"[Get Started](get-started.md): build, run, use the hybrid CLI, tools,\n"
"approvals, skills, resume, trace, and tests."
msgstr ""
"[快速开始](get-started.md)：构建、运行、使用混合 CLI、工具、审批、技能、恢复、"
"追踪和测试。"

msgid ""
"[Architecture](architecture.md): runtime layers, main execution flow, crate\n"
"boundaries, and current architecture contracts."
msgstr ""
"[架构](architecture.md)：运行时层次、主执行流、crate 边界和当前架构契约。"

msgid ""
"[Hybrid File References](hybrid-file-references.md): interactive `@path`\n"
"suggestions and workspace indexing."
msgstr ""
"[混合文件引用](hybrid-file-references.md)：交互式 `@path` 建议与工作区索引。"

msgid ""
"[Hybrid Slash Commands](hybrid-slash-commands.md): interactive `/` command\n"
"suggestions and completion behavior."
msgstr ""
"[混合斜杠命令](hybrid-slash-commands.md)：交互式 `/` 命令建议与补全行为。"

msgid ""
"[Hybrid Input Editing](hybrid-input-editing.md): cursor movement, delete\n"
"shortcuts, and multiline prompt behavior."
msgstr ""
"[混合输入编辑](hybrid-input-editing.md)：光标移动、删除快捷键和多行提示行为。"

msgid ""
"[Target Architecture](target-architecture.md): long-term agent, model, tools,\n"
"security, storage, observability, and UX goals."
msgstr ""
"[目标架构](target-architecture.md)：长期的 agent、模型、工具、安全、存储、可观测性"
"和 UX 目标。"

msgid "[Download](download.md): how to obtain and build Unio."
msgstr "[下载](download.md)：如何获取和构建 Unio。"

msgid "[Site Operations](site-operations.md): local preview, CI, and GitHub Pages."
msgstr "[站点运维](site-operations.md)：本地预览、CI 和 GitHub Pages。"

msgid ""
"[Decisions](decisions/0001-start-from-zero.md): architecture decision records."
msgstr "[决策记录](decisions/0001-start-from-zero.md)：架构决策记录。"

msgid ""
"Keep docs and implementation synchronized. Update `PLAN.md`, `README.md`,\n"
"`CHANGE.md`, and the relevant `docs/` file when behavior changes."
msgstr ""
"保持文档与实现同步。行为变更时更新 `PLAN.md`、`README.md`、`CHANGE.md` 以及相关的 "
"`docs/` 文件。"

