# download.md
msgid "Pre-built Binaries"
msgstr "预构建二进制"

msgid "Download the latest release for your platform:"
msgstr "下载适合您平台的最新版本："

msgid "Platform"
msgstr "平台"

msgid "Architecture"
msgstr "架构"

msgid "Archive"
msgstr "归档包"

msgid "Each archive contains two binaries:"
msgstr "每个归档包含两个二进制文件："

msgid "For all releases and changelogs visit the"
msgstr "访问以下链接查看所有版本和更新日志："

