# site-operations.md
msgid "Site Operations"
msgstr "站点运维"

msgid ""
"This page describes how to build, preview, and deploy the Unio documentation\n"
"site locally and through GitHub Actions."
msgstr "本页说明如何在本地及通过 GitHub Actions 构建、预览和部署 Unio 文档站点。"

msgid "Local Preview"
msgstr "本地预览"

msgid "Install mdBook:"
msgstr "安装 mdBook："

msgid "Build and serve the site locally:"
msgstr "在本地构建并提供服务："

msgid ""
"Open `http://localhost:3000` in a browser. The server reloads on file changes."
msgstr "在浏览器中打开 `http://localhost:3000`。服务器在文件变更时自动重载。"

msgid "To only build without serving:"
msgstr "仅构建不启动服务："

msgid ""
"Output is placed in `docs/book/`. This directory is excluded from version\n"
"control via `.gitignore`."
msgstr "输出位于 `docs/book/`，该目录已通过 `.gitignore` 排除在版本控制之外。"

msgid "CI Workflow"
msgstr "CI 工作流"

msgid ""
"The `.github/workflows/deploy-site.yml` workflow runs on every push to the\n"
"default branch and on `workflow_dispatch`."
msgstr "`.github/workflows/deploy-site.yml` 工作流在每次推送到默认分支或触发 `workflow_dispatch` 时运行。"

msgid "Steps performed by the workflow:"
msgstr "工作流执行步骤："

msgid "GitHub Pages Setup"
msgstr "GitHub Pages 配置"

msgid "Enable Pages for the repository:"
msgstr "为仓库启用 Pages："

msgid "Build Artifacts"
msgstr "构建产物"

msgid ""
"The workflow artifact is `github-pages` uploaded from `docs/book/`. The\n"
"`deploy-pages` action publishes it under the repository Pages URL."
msgstr ""
"工作流产物 `github-pages` 从 `docs/book/` 上传，`deploy-pages` action 将其发布到"
"仓库的 Pages URL 下。"

msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr "故障排查"

msgid "Symptom"
msgstr "现象"

msgid "Check"
msgstr "检查项"

